    <title>如何优雅地制作表格</title>
    <link href="https://passing-j.github.io/2017/03/07/dataTables/"/>
    <id>https://passing-j.github.io/2017/03/07/dataTables/</id>
    <published>2017-03-07T07:56:50.414Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-07T14:24:04.946Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>用简单的方式实现表格布局、从后台获取数据渲染到页面。</p>
<h3 id="需要具备的基础知识"><a href="#需要具备的基础知识" class="headerlink" title="需要具备的基础知识"></a>需要具备的基础知识</h3><p>HTML、CSS、BootStrap、jQuery</p>
<h3 id="用到的主要工具"><a href="#用到的主要工具" class="headerlink" title="用到的主要工具"></a>用到的主要工具</h3><p>jQuery的 <a href="https://datatables.net/" target="_blank" rel="external">DataTables.js</a> 插件</p>
<h3 id="实例1"><a href="#实例1" class="headerlink" title="实例1"></a>实例1</h3><p>一张基础表单<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;!-- 头部引入链接 --&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;link rel=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> href=<span class="string">"css/bootstrap.css"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;link rel=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> href=<span class="string">"css/plugins/dataTables/datatables.min.css"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;!-- 尾部引入链接 --&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"js/jquery-2.1.1.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"js/bootstrap.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"js/plugins/dataTables/datatables.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>body部分<br>参数”.display”定义了基本的控件<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;table id=<span class="string">"example"</span> class=<span class="string">"display table table-striped table-bordered table-hover"</span> cellspacing=<span class="string">"0"</span> width=<span class="string">"100%"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;thead&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;tr&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Name&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Position&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Office&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Age&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Start date&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Salary&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;/tr&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/thead&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;tfoot&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;tr&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Name&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Position&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Office&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Age&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Start date&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;th&gt;Salary&lt;/th&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;/tr&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/tfoot&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;tbody&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;tr&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;Tiger Nixon&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;System Architect&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;Edinburgh&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            ...</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;New York&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;27&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;2011/01/25&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">            &lt;td&gt;<span class="variable">$112</span>,000&lt;/td&gt;</div><div class="line">        &lt;/tr&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/tbody&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/table&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>css部分<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">table thead &#123;</div><div class="line">    background-color: <span class="comment">#1AB394;</span></div><div class="line">    color: white;</div><div class="line">    font-size: 12px;</div><div class="line">    font-weight: bold;</div><div class="line">    white-space: nowrap;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>js部分<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$(document).ready(<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">    $(<span class="string">'#example'</span>).DataTable();</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="效果图1"><a href="#效果图1" class="headerlink" title="效果图1"></a>效果图1</h3><p><img src="/images/1table/table.jpg" alt="基本效果图" width="80%" align="center"></p>
<h3 id="实例2"><a href="#实例2" class="headerlink" title="实例2"></a>实例2</h3><p>把控件部分改为中文，只需改动js部分的参数<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$(document).ready(<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">    $(<span class="string">'#example'</span>).DataTable(&#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"oLanguage"</span>: &#123; //下面是一些汉语翻译</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"sSearch"</span>: <span class="string">"搜索"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"sLengthMenu"</span>: <span class="string">"每页显示 _MENU_ 条记录"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"sZeroRecords"</span>: <span class="string">"没有检索到数据"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"sInfo"</span>: <span class="string">"显示 _START_ 至 _END_ 条 &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;共 _TOTAL_ 条"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"sInfoFiltered"</span>: <span class="string">"(筛选自 _MAX_ 条数据)"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"sInfoEmtpy"</span>: <span class="string">"没有数据"</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"sProcessing"</span>: <span class="string">"正在加载数据..."</span>,</div><div class="line">            <span class="string">"oPaginate"</span>: &#123;</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"sFirst"</span>: <span class="string">"首页"</span>,</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"sPrevious"</span>: <span class="string">"前一页"</span>,</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"sNext"</span>: <span class="string">"后一页"</span>,</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"sLast"</span>: <span class="string">"末页"</span></div><div class="line">            &#125;</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;);</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="效果图2"><a href="#效果图2" class="headerlink" title="效果图2"></a>效果图2</h3><p><img src="/images/1table/table2.jpg" alt="中文效果图" width="80%" align="center"></p>
<h3 id="实例3"><a href="#实例3" class="headerlink" title="实例3"></a>实例3</h3><p>表头固定，沿Y轴滚动，类似Excel<br>同样只需改动js部分的参数<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$(<span class="string">'#example'</span>).DataTable(&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="string">"scrollY"</span>: <span class="string">"300px"</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="string">"paging"</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">    <span class="string">"oLanguage"</span>: &#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="string">"sSearch"</span>: <span class="string">"搜索"</span>,</div><div class="line">        ...</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="效果图3"><a href="#效果图3" class="headerlink" title="效果图3"></a>效果图3</h3><p><img src="/images/1table/table3.jpg" alt="固定表头效果图" width="80%" align="center"></p>
<h3 id="实例4"><a href="#实例4" class="headerlink" title="实例4"></a>实例4</h3><p>从后台获取数据<br>body部分改为<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;table id=<span class="string">"example"</span> class=<span class="string">"display table table-striped table-bordered table-hover"</span> cellspacing=<span class="string">"0"</span> width=<span class="string">"100%"</span>&gt;&lt;/table&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>是的，就只有一个table标签</p>
<p>js部分变化有点多<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$(document).ready(<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">    $.ajax(&#123;</div><div class="line">        <span class="built_in">type</span>: <span class="string">"GET"</span>,</div><div class="line">        url: <span class="string">"music.json"</span>,</div><div class="line">        success: <span class="keyword">function</span>(data) &#123;</div><div class="line">            var t = data.title;</div><div class="line">            var d = data.data;</div><div class="line">            $(<span class="string">'#example'</span>).DataTable(&#123;</div><div class="line">                //渲染表格</div><div class="line">                data: d,</div><div class="line">                //渲染表头</div><div class="line">                columns: [&#123;</div><div class="line">                    title: t[0]</div><div class="line">                &#125;, &#123;</div><div class="line">                    title: t[1]</div><div class="line">                &#125;, &#123;</div><div class="line">                    title: t[2]</div><div class="line">                &#125;, &#123;</div><div class="line">                    title: t[3]</div><div class="line">                &#125;, &#123;</div><div class="line">                    title: t[4]</div><div class="line">                &#125;, &#123;</div><div class="line">                    title: t[5]</div><div class="line">                &#125;],</div><div class="line">                <span class="string">"oLanguage"</span>: &#123; //下面是一些汉语翻译</div><div class="line">                    <span class="string">"sSearch"</span>: <span class="string">"搜索"</span>,</div><div class="line">                    <span class="string">"sLengthMenu"</span>: <span class="string">"每页显示 _MENU_ 条记录"</span>,</div><div class="line">                    ...</div><div class="line">                &#125;</div><div class="line">            &#125;);</div><div class="line">            //表头背景色,此行解决表头失色问题</div><div class="line">            $(<span class="string">'table:eq(0) th'</span>).css(<span class="string">"background-color"</span>, <span class="string">"#1AB394"</span>);</div><div class="line">        &#125;</div><div class="line">    &#125;);</div><div class="line">&#125;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>后台JSON数据格式<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"title"</span>: [<span class="string">"Name"</span>,<span class="string">"Position"</span>,<span class="string">"Office"</span>,<span class="string">"Extn"</span>,<span class="string">"Start date"</span>,<span class="string">"Salary"</span>],</div><div class="line">  <span class="string">"data"</span>: [</div><div class="line">    [</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"Tiger Nixon"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"System Architect"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"Edinburgh"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"5421"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"2011/04/25"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$320</span>,800"</span></div><div class="line">    ],</div><div class="line">    [</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"Garrett Winters"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"Accountant"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"Tokyo"</span>,</div><div class="line">      ...</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"4226"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"2011/01/25"</span>,</div><div class="line">      <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$112</span>,000"</span></div><div class="line">    ]</div><div class="line">  ]</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="效果图4"><a href="#效果图4" class="headerlink" title="效果图4"></a>效果图4</h3><p><img src="/images/1table/table4.jpg" alt="后台引用效果图" width="80%" align="center"></p>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>在工作中能快速制作能看得过去的表格，能和后台进行数据交互，更多实例详见 <a href="https://datatables.net/examples/index" target="_blank" rel="external">DataTables</a> 官网。</p>
]]></content>
    
